WEBVTT

00:13:28.805 --> 00:13:34.551
It makes us see ourselves
as far more beautiful than we really are.

00:13:34.575 --> 00:13:36.042
This is the seduction.

00:13:36.424 --> 00:13:38.871
But if you really know yourself,

00:13:38.895 --> 00:13:42.363
you will not fall
for this kind of flattery.

00:13:42.879 --> 00:13:46.942
If somebody puts a mirror
in front of your eyes

00:13:46.966 --> 00:13:52.026
that hides all your ugly bits
and makes you see yourself

00:13:52.050 --> 00:13:56.334
as far more beautiful
and far more important

00:13:56.358 --> 00:13:57.949
than you really are,

00:13:57.973 --> 00:14:00.837
just break that mirror.